# Related Packs
related_packs:
  - id: MATH-101
    relationship: "Mathematics is the language of physics; algebra and calculus enable quantitative modeling"

  - id: SCI-101
    relationship: "Scientific method and experimental reasoning are the methodological backbone"

  - id: CHEM-101
    relationship: "Chemistry extends atomic structure and thermodynamics from physics"

  - id: ASTRO-101
    relationship: "Astronomy applies gravity, light, and nuclear physics on cosmic scales"

  - id: ENGR-101
    relationship: "Engineering is applied physics; every structure and device uses physics principles"

  - id: CODE-101
    relationship: "Physics simulations deepen understanding of both physics and programming"

